g.text: Packages are used to hold requirements.
Packages can also be composed of other
packages for form of nesting of requirements
Requirements can be decomposed into ther
requirements. This is not defined as a composition
relationship in the metamodel, instead it will be
handled through the syntax and validation rules. This is
to allow requirements to be connected via relationship
arrows as opposed to being contained within the box.
This is a constraint imposed by the Sirius development
